data.description: In Sunbrooke, a charming community located in St. Cloud, you will find this beautiful 3 bedroom and 2 bathroom property in excellent condition. The house features a Great Room for a large family and was built in 2022, so it is like new. Additionally, this property is located near great schools and shopping.    The House features Solar Panels, making it energy-efficient and environmentally friendly. Upon entering the house, you will be greeted by ample natural light. The house features a modern kitchen with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and expansive living space. The master bedroom offers a generous private bath complete with a double sink vanity, a spacious shower, and a walk-in closet. The backyard is private and fenced, perfect for enjoying the outdoors. The house also features a front porch and a 2-car garage.
